							# [R2-8 boot-test] SUCCESSION laws area — the #312 female-line succession_law group
							# (agnatic / agnatic-cognatic / absolute-cognatic) was never listed in this hand-built
							# laws view (which OVERRIDES upstream's — upstream has NO succession area), so it did not
							# appear; groups must be listed explicitly. Added here so ALL THREE tiers live in the Laws
							# tab under one header. The old GC-Edicts reform strip + the absolute_cognatic_succession
							# country-modifier + the succession_reform_* decision guis are retired — Absolute-Cognatic
							# is now a real law tier carrying its own modifier (00_succession_laws.txt).
